<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span12 profile-heading">
            <h2 class="pull-left">Domain verwalten</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span12">
            <form novalidate name="domainForm" class="simple-form" ng-class="{clean: formclean, unclean: !formclean}">
                <tabset>
                    <tab active="tab1.active">
                        <tab-heading>Schritt 1</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container" ng-form="step1form">
                            <h3>Domain [[ domain.name ]]<br>Standard-Banner-Konfiguration</h3>
                            <div class="horizontal-radio-group">
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="forwardRadio"
                                    ng-model="formData.forwarding"
                                    dh-value="true"

                                    dh-label="Weiterleitung einrichten"
                                ></dh-input>
                                <dh-input
                                    type="radio"

                                    dh-name="forwardRadio"
                                    ng-model="formData.forwarding"
                                    dh-value="false"

                                    dh-label="keine Weiterleitung"
                                ></dh-input>
                                <div style="clear: both;"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div ng-show="formData.forwarding == 'true'">
                                <dh-input
                                    class="span6"
                                    type="url"

                                    dh-name="targetName"
                                    ng-model="banner.redirect_domain"

                                    dh-ng-required="formData.forwarding == 'true'"

                                    dh-label="Zieldomain eingeben"

                                    dh-tooltip="Bitte geben Sie eine g체ltige URL ein."
                                    dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                    dh-tooltip-placement="right"
                                    dh-tooltip-invalid="Bitte geben Sie eine g체ltige URL ein."
                                ></dh-input>
                            </div>
                            <label for="languages">In welcher Sprache soll der Banner angezeigt werden</label>
                            <dh-select class="span6" ng-model="banner.language" dh-options="languages"></dh-select>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                <button style="visibility: hidden"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zur체ck</button>
                                <button>&nbsp;Vorschau ansehen</button>
                                <button class="pull-right next" ng-click="nextStep(tab2, step1form)"><i class="icon-tick-right icon-white pull-right"></i>Weiter&nbsp;</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                    <tab active="tab2.active" disabled="!step1form.$valid">
                        <tab-heading>Schritt 2</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container" ng-form="step2form">
                            <h3>Domain [[ domain.name ]]<br>Standard-Banner-Konfiguration</h3>
                            <p>Welcher Banner soll dem User beim Besuch von [[ domain.name ]] angezeigt werden?</p>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span3 position-radio-container">
                                    <label for="positionRadioCenter" class="position-label center"></label>
                                    <dh-input
                                        type="radio"

                                        dh-name="positionRadio"
                                        ng-model="banner.position"
                                        dh-value="center"
                                        dh-id="positionRadioCenter"

                                        dh-label="mittig"

                                        dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                        dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                        dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                        dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                    ></dh-input>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span3 position-radio-container">
                                    <label for="positionRadioTop" class="position-label top"></label>
                                    <dh-input
                                        type="radio"

                                        dh-name="positionRadio"
                                        ng-model="banner.position"
                                        dh-value="top"
                                        dh-id="positionRadioTop"

                                        dh-label="oben"

                                        dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                        dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                        dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                        dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                    ></dh-input>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span3 position-radio-container">
                                    <label for="positionRadioRight" class="position-label right"></label>
                                    <dh-input
                                        type="radio"

                                        dh-name="positionRadio"
                                        ng-model="banner.position"
                                        dh-value="right"
                                        dh-id="positionRadioRight"

                                        dh-label="rechts"

                                        dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                        dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                        dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                        dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                    ></dh-input>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <dh-input
                                type="checkbox"

                                dh-name="secondvisitBox"
                                ng-model="formData.secondvisit"
                                dh-value="true"

                                dh-label="Ab dem 2. Besuch t채glich soll ein anderer Banner angezeigt werden."

                                dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                            ></dh-input>
                            <div class="fluid-row clearfix" ng-show="formData.secondvisit == true">
                                <div class="span3 position-radio-container">
                                    <label for="altPositionRadioTop" class="position-label center"></label>
                                    <dh-input
                                        type="radio"

                                        dh-name="secondpositionRadio"
                                        ng-model="banner.position_alternative"
                                        dh-value="top"
                                        dh-id="altPositionRadioTop"

                                        dh-label="oben"

                                        dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                        dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                        dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                        dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                    ></dh-input>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span3 position-radio-container">
                                    <label for="altPositionRadioRight" class="position-label right"></label>
                                    <dh-input
                                        type="radio"

                                        dh-name="secondpositionRadio"
                                        ng-model="banner.position_alternative"
                                        dh-value="right"
                                        dh-id="altPositionRadioRight"

                                        dh-label="rechts"

                                        dh-tooltip="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.default' | translate ]]"
                                        dh-tooltip-trigger="focus"
                                        dh-tooltip-placement="top"
                                        dh-tooltip-invalid="[[ 'login.form.username.tooltip.invalid' | translate ]]"
                                    ></dh-input>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                <button ng-click="tab1.active = true"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zur체ck</button>
                                <button style="visibility: hidden">&nbsp;Vorschau ansehen</button>
                                <button class="pull-right next" ng-click="submit(tab3)"><i class="icon-tick-right icon-white pull-right"></i>Speichern&nbsp;</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                    <tab active="tab3.active" disabled="!(step1form.$valid && step2form.$valid)" select="submit(tab3)">
                        <tab-heading>Finalisieren</tab-heading>
                        <div class="tab-content-container">
                            <h3>Die Einstellungen f체r [[ domainName ]] wurden erfolgreich gespeichert!</h3>
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus. Morbi et massa at elit tempus pellentesque nec ut eros. Vestibulum auctor enim eget aliquet porttitor. Nulla lacinia purus non elementum commodo.</p>
                            <div class="row-fluid">
                                <div class="span4 offset2">
                                    <h4>M철glichkeit 1:<br>Aktivieren bei dotHIV</h4>
                                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus.</p>
                                     <button>Jetzt aktivieren</button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="span4">
                                    <h4>M철glichkeit 2:<br>Code downloaden</h4>
                                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Duis scelerisque neque id viverra mollis. Sed mi sem, consequat eu ultrices non, imperdiet id tellus.</p>
                                     <button>Jetzt downloaden</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tab-bottom-buttons">
                                    <button ng-click="tab2.active = true"><i class="icon-tick-left"></i>&nbsp;Schritt zur체ck</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </tab>
                </tabset>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
